聆听多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) 与保罗·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 和林戈·斯塔尔 (Ringo Starr) 合作翻唱的《Let It Be》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-dolly-partons-let-it-be-cover-with-paul-mccartney-and-ringo-starr-3484970?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=与保罗·麦卡特尼和林戈·斯塔尔一起聆听多莉·帕顿的歌曲《让它成为封面》Will Richards Fri, 18 Aug 2023 07:29:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3484970 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="多莉·帕顿" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>米克·弗利特伍德和彼得·弗兰普顿也出现在众星云集的封面上</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-dolly-partons-let-it-be-cover-with-paul-mccartney-and-ringo-starr-3484970">保罗·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 和林戈·斯塔尔 (Ringo Starr) 与多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) 合作翻唱《听多莉·帕顿》 (Listen to Dolly Parton) 的《Let It Be》一文</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="多莉·帕顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dolly-macca-ringo-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">多莉·帕顿</a>分享了她翻唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>的《Let It Be》，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-fleetwood">米克·弗利特伍德</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-frampton">彼得·弗兰普顿</a>合作 - 请听下面。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-to-share-let-it-be-cover-featuring-paul-mccartney-ringo-starr-mick-fleetwood-and-peter-frampton-this-week-3483123">这首歌于本周早些时候被宣布</a>为帕顿即将推出的第 49 张个人录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-partons-rock-album-will-feature-covers-of-prince-the-rolling-stones-led-zeppelin-and-more-3361240">“Rockstar”</a>的最新预览。</p><p>帕顿此前分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">皇后</a>乐队即将发行的专辑中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-dolly-partons-triumphant-cover-of-queen-we-are-the-champions-3473765">《我们是冠军》</a>的翻唱。</p><p>接下来是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">Judas Priest</a>的 Rob Halford 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motley-crue">Mötley Crüe</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nikki-sixx">Nikki Sixx</a>翻唱的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-teams-up-with-judas-priests-rob-halford-and-motley-crue-nikki-sixx-on-new-song-3457153">《Bygones》</a> ，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heart">Heart</a>的 Ann Wilson 翻唱的《Magic Man》以及《World On Fire》。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-has-revealed-tracklist-rockstar-album-3441326">5 月宣布的</a>《Rockstar》将收录 9 首原创歌曲和 21 首翻唱摇滚经典歌曲，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prince">Prince</a>的《Purple Rain》、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队的</a>《(I Can&#39;t Get No) Satisfaction》等。</p><p>这张唱片以两首翻唱结束：《Let It Be》和《Free Bird》，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lynyrd-skynyrd">Lynyrd Skynyrd</a>成员加里·罗辛顿 (Gary Rossington) 和阿蒂姆斯·派尔 (Artimus Pyle) 演唱，后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lynyrd-skynyrd-founding-guitarist-gary-rossington-dies-aged-71-3408659">已于 3 月去世</a>，死后由罗尼·范·赞特 (Ronnie Van Zandt) 演唱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="多莉·帕顿 (Dolly Parton) - Let It Be（保罗·麦卡特尼 &amp; 林戈·斯塔尔）（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dXW-p4nKdDA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Rockstar》将于 11 月 17 日通过 Butterfly/Big Machine 发行。<a href="https://shop.dollyparton.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>预订专辑。</p><p> “我很高兴终于推出我的第一张摇滚专辑《Rockstar》！”帕顿在一份声明中说道。</p><p> “我非常荣幸能够与一些有史以来最伟大的标志性歌手和音乐家合作，并且能够演唱整张专辑中的所有标志性歌曲，这是一种无法估量的快乐。我希望每个人都喜欢这张专辑，就像我喜欢将它组合在一起一样！”</p><h3> <strong>“摇滚明星”曲目列表</strong></h3><p><strong>1.“摇滚明星”（特邀嘉宾里奇·桑博拉）</strong><br /> <strong>2.《战火世界》</strong><br /> <strong>3.“你的每一次呼吸”（壮举。斯汀）</strong><br /> <strong>4.“张开双臂”（壮举。史蒂夫·佩里）</strong><br /> <strong>5.“Magic Man”（壮举。安·威尔逊与特邀嘉宾霍华德·利斯）</strong><br /> <strong>6.“只要我能看到光明”（壮举。约翰·福格蒂）</strong><br /> <strong>7.“要么或者”（壮举。Kid Rock）</strong><br /> <strong>8.“I Want You Back”（壮举。史蒂文·泰勒与特邀嘉宾沃伦·海恩斯）</strong><br /> <strong>9.“What Has Rock And Roll Ever Done For You”（壮举。Stevie Nicks 与特邀嘉宾 Waddy Wachtel）</strong><br /> <strong>10.《紫雨》</strong><br /> <strong>11.“宝贝，我爱你的方式”（壮举。彼得·弗兰普顿）</strong><br /> <strong>12.“我恨自己爱你”（壮举。琼·杰特和黑心乐队）</strong><br /> <strong>13.“Night Moves”（克里斯·斯泰普尔顿）</strong><br /> <strong>14.“Wrecking Ball”（壮举。麦莉·赛勒斯）</strong><br /> <strong>15.“（我无法得到）满足”（壮举。P！nk和布兰迪·卡莱尔）</strong><br /> <strong>16.“继续爱你”（壮举。凯文·克罗宁）</s