利佐的“Big Grrl”舞者在新的公开信中称赞她“打破限制” https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzos-big-grrl-dancers-praise-her-for-shattering-limitations-in-new-open-letter-3484966?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lizzos-大舞者在新公开信中称赞她打破了限制Will RichardsFri, 18 Aug 2023 07:01:21 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3484966 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lizzo 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们非常荣幸能够与如此出色的人才同台演出”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzos-big-grrl-dancers-praise-her-for-shattering-limitations-in-new-open-letter-3484966">Lizzo 的“Big Grrl”舞者在新的公开信中赞扬她“打破限制”，该公开信</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lizzo 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/lIzzo-getty-Joseph-Okpako-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在持续的法律诉讼中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">Lizzo</a>的“Big Grrl”和“Big Boiiis”舞者在一封新的公开信中赞扬了这位歌手。</p><p>上个月，据透露，这位歌手正<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-sued-by-backup-dancers-for-sexual-harassment-and-creating-hostile-work-environment-3476570">被她的三名前舞者起诉，他们指控她性骚扰和充满敌意的工作环境</a>。</p><p>克里斯托·威廉姆斯 (Crystal Williams)、阿里安娜·戴维斯 (Arianna Davis) 和诺埃尔·罗德里格斯 (Noelle Rodriguez) 指控利佐营造敌对的工作环境并进行性骚扰等指控。她的舞蹈队队长 Shirlene Quigley 和制作公司 Big Grrrl Big Touring Inc. 也被列为诉讼的被告。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-responds-to-sexual-harassment-lawsuit-im-hurt-3477714">利佐随后回应称，这些“耸人听闻”的指控“伤害了”她</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-hires-former-billy-cosby-lawyer-for-sexual-harassment-lawsuit-3478228">聘请了马蒂·辛格(Marty Singer)</a>律师，他曾处理过最近针对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jonah-hill-ex-girlfriend-sarah-brady-allegations-emotionally-abusive-3466903">乔纳·希尔</a>(Jonah Hill)、约翰尼·德普( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depp-amber-heard-jury-reaches-verdict-3238472">Johnny Depp</a> )、比尔·科斯比( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bill-cosby-found-guilty-sexaully-assaulting-girl-playboy-mansion-3252989">Bill Cosby</a> )等人的案件。</p><p>在利佐的“特别巡演”结束后，她剩下的舞者——被称为“Big Grrrls”和“Big Boiiis”——发表了一份赞扬这位歌手的声明。<br />声明感谢利佐“[创建]一个平台，让我们能够将我们的激情与目标相结合。</p><p> “我们在特别之旅中度过了一生中最美好的时光，”它补充道。信中写道：“我们非常荣幸能够与如此出色的人才同台演出。” “对品格和文化的承诺优先于每一个动作和时刻，这是我们可能要求的最伟大的教训和祝福之一。”</p><p>它还赞扬 Lizzo“打破了限制，为 Big Grrrrl 和 Big Boiii 舞者们打开了大门，让他们可以做我们喜欢的事情……不仅是为了我们，也为了女性和所有打破障碍的人。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwDTxt7snED/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 