23/08/gi-dle-88rising-heat-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gi-dle">(G)I-DLE</a>即将推出的首张全英文 EP &#39;HEAT&#39; 已被推迟。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/gidle-i-feel-queencard-review-3444985">(G)I-DLE – “I Feel”评论：注定是他们迄今为止最具争议的版本</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，(G)I-DLE 透露他们将于 9 月与 88rising 合作发行他们的首张全英文 EP“HEAT”。不久前，他们的厂牌<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cube-entertainment">CUBE Entertainment</a>与专注于亚洲的音乐公司 88rising 建立了新的合作伙伴关系。</p><p>今天（8月18日），88rising宣布与CUBE Entertainment决定推迟发行《HEAT》。 “我们正在努力对 EP 进行最后的润色，以确保为世界各地的 (G)I-DLE 粉丝提供最好的质量，”他们补充道。</p><p> 《HEAT》现将于太平洋标准时间 10 月 5 日下午 5 点/韩国标准时间 10 月 6 日上午 9 点发行，比原定发行时间晚一个月。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zxx" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://t.co/KgI38MSbiV">pic.twitter.com/KgI38MSbiV</a></p><p> - 88rising (@88rising) <a href="https://twitter.com/88rising/status/1692355768459333732?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 18 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> 7月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gi-dle-english-single-i-do-3467196">(G)I-DLE发行了《HEAT》的首张单曲《I Do》</a> 。这首歌与一段叙事性很强的音乐视频一起发布，该视频讲述了一个外星人爱上人类的故事。</p><p> 《I Do》的第二部音乐视频现已发布，由 GMMTV 2021 年浪漫剧集<em>《F4 泰国：花样男子》</em>中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gi-dle-music-video-i-do-f4-thailand-boys-over-flowers-stars-3472838">“Tu”Tontawan Tantivejakul 和“Dew”Jirawat Sutivanisak 主演</a>。</p><p> (G)I-DLE 也是最新开始与 88rising 合作的韩国流行音乐艺人。这家专注于亚洲的音乐公司还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jackson-wang">王嘉尔</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bibi">BIBI</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chung-ha">Chung Ha</a>等音乐人建立了合作关系。</p><p>在(G)I-DLE的其他新闻中，成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miyeon">Miyeon</a>最近被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gi-dle-miyeon-jimmy-choo-newest-global-brand-ambassador-3476838">任命为Jimmy Choo最新的全球品牌大使</a>。作为合作伙伴关系的一部分，这位韩国流行偶像将出现在这家英国奢侈时尚品牌 2023 年秋季广告活动中。</p><p>与此同时，该女团将于 9 月初开始 2023 年“I am FREE-TY”世界巡演的欧洲站。它将在伦敦、巴黎、柏林等地演出。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gi-dle-2023-world-tour-i-am-free-ty-dates-venues-tickets-3436259">在这里获取门票</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gi-dle-delay-release-of-first-english-ep-heat-3484884">(G)I-DLE 延迟发行后首张英文 EP《HEAT》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 FIFTY FIFTY 在针对其唱片公司 Attrakt 的诉讼中打破沉默https://www.nme.com/news/music/fifty-fifty-break-silence-lawsuit-against-management-attract-3484734?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fifty-fifty-break-silence-lawsuit-against-管理吸引Puah ZiweiFri, 18 Aug 2023 02:33:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3484734 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="五十五十抖音丘比特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该女团在声明中声称“媒体报道了许多不实的故事”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fifty-fifty-break-silence-lawsuit-against-management-attract-3484734">《五十五十》打破沉默，对他们的唱片公司 Attrakt 提起诉讼，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="五十五十抖音丘比特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/FIFTY-FIFTY-Credit-ATTRAKT-Creative-Content-Group@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自针对唱片公司 Attrakt 提起诉讼以来，韩国流行女团<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fifty-fifty">FIFTY FIFTY</a>首次公开发言。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/barbie-soundtrack-mark-ronson-interview-3473687">马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 如何成为好莱坞配乐之王：“‘芭比娃娃’感觉很特别”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 8 月 17 日，据称来自 FIFTY FIFTY 的英文和韩文手写声明被发布在一个全新的 Instagram 帐户上，没有个人资料照片。据<a href="https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=112&amp;aid=0003648325" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Herald Pop</em></a>报道，该女子组合的一名代表随后证实这些信件确实是由成员们写的。</p><p>五十五十在信中表示，由于“当前的媒体和新闻报道令人困惑”，他们决定“放下犹豫，站出来表明我们的立场”。</p><p> “误解和指责不断增加。我们对此深感震惊，并经历了一段艰难的时期，”四人写道。 “我们相信，尽管存在这些困难，但仍有一个真相需要揭开。”</p><p>他们补充说：“我们首先想借此机会纠正我们与该机构的关系中被迫犯下的错误。”并表示，为了“保护我们的音乐”，他们“别无选择”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3421455" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3421455" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3421455" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/fifty-fifty-cupid-hot-100.jpg" alt="五五十丘比特" width="2000" height="1271" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/fifty-fifty-cupid-hot-100.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/fifty-fifty-cupid-hot-100-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/fifty-fifty-cupid-hot-100-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/fifty-fifty-cupid-hot-100-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/fifty-fifty-cupid-hot-100-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/fifty-fifty-cupid-hot-100-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3421455" class="wp-caption-text">五十分五十。图片来源：Attrakt</figcaption></figure><p> 《五十五十》随后声称“媒体报道了许多不真实的故事”，但他们没有具体提及哪些新闻报道。 “我们在发表评论时一直很谨慎……[但这并不意味着我们承认或接受所报道的内容”。</p><p> “我们认为，基于事实将此事告上法庭是解决问题的正确途径。我们希望在审判过程中真相大白，我们的权利能够得到保障。”他们补充道。</p><p> The girl group say that they have “[continued] to collect and submit materials and evidence based on facts”, and hope that the public “look at the facts [of the situation] objectively”.</p><p> FIFTY FIFTY ended their statement by reiterating that “every one of our members is in this together, relying on each other to stand strong”. They added that their intention is to continue as a girl group “in a trustworthy environment”. </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwCyol8hb5f/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div styl